### 2. `src/components/counselor/ReminderModal.tsx`
A modal that pops up when a counselor clicks **"Set Reminder"** on a lead card.

#### UI Design:
```
┌──────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  🔔 Set Follow-up Reminder              │
│  ─────────────────────────────────────   │
│  Lead: JOHN DOE (LEAD-ABC-1001)          │
│  Score: 🔥 HOT                           │
│                                          │
│  📅 Reminder Date & Time                 │
│  ┌──────────────────────────────────┐    │
│  │ 2026-04-30T10:00:00             │    │
│  └──────────────────────────────────┘    │
│                                          │
│  📝 Follow-up Note (optional)            │
│  ┌──────────────────────────────────┐    │
│  │ Call again about MBA program     │    │
│  │                                  │    │
│  └──────────────────────────────────┘    │
│                                          │
│  [ Cancel ]              [ Set Reminder ] │
└──────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

#### Props:
```typescript
interface ReminderModalProps {
  isOpen: boolean;
  onClose: () => void;
  leadId: string;
  leadName: string;
  leadScore: string;
  existingReminder?: Reminder; // For edit mode (PUT /{id})
  onSuccess: () => void;       // Refresh parent after create/edit
}
```

#### Behavior:
- **Create mode**: Calls `POST /api/reminders/lead/{leadId}`
- **Edit mode**: Pre-fills fields, calls `PUT /api/reminders/{reminderId}`
- Date picker defaults to **tomorrow at 10:00 AM**
- Shows toast on success/failure
- Uses `LoadingButton` component (already exists at `ui/LoadingButton.tsx`)

---

### 3. `src/components/counselor/ReminderDashboard.tsx`
A full-page view showing all of the counselor's reminders with **tabbed navigation**.

#### UI Design:
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  🔔 My Reminders                                            │
│                                                              │
│  [ 🔴 Due (3) ] [ ⚠️ Missed (1) ] [ ⏳ Pending (5) ] [ All ] │
│  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────   │
│                                                              │
│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐    │
│  │ 🔥 HOT  │  JOHN DOE           │  Apr 30, 10:00 AM  │    │
│  │         │  "Call about MBA"    │  [ 👁 Seen ] [✏️] [🗑]│    │
│  ├─────────┼────────────────────  ┼────────────────────┤    │
│  │ ❄️ COLD │  JANE SMITH          │  May 02, 02:00 PM  │    │
│  │         │  "Email documents"   │  [ 👁 Seen ] [✏️] [🗑]│    │
│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘    │
│                                                              │
│  Score Filter: [ All ] [ HOT ] [ WARM ] [ COLD ]             │
│                                                              │
│  ← Prev   Page 1 / 3   Next →                               │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

#### Tabs:
| Tab | API Call | Description |
|---|---|---|
| **Due** | `GET /me/due/page/{p}/size/{s}` | Triggered reminders — counselor hasn't acknowledged yet |
| **Missed** | `GET /me/missed/page/{p}/size/{s}` | Past-due — needs immediate attention (shown in red) |
| **Pending** | `GET /me/pending/page/{p}/size/{s}` | Future reminders — scheduled but not triggered |
| **All** | `GET /me/{page}/{size}` | Complete history across all states |

#### Each Reminder Card Actions:
| Button | Action | API |
|---|---|---|
| 👁 **Mark Seen** | Acknowledge alert (removes from Due tab) | `PUT /{id}/seen` |
| ✏️ **Edit** | Opens `ReminderModal` in edit mode | Pre-fills modal → `PUT /{id}` |
| 🗑 **Cancel** | Removes reminder with confirmation dialog | `DELETE /{id}` |

#### Score Filter:
- Dropdown or pill buttons: `All` / `HOT` / `WARM` / `COLD` / `INTERESTED` / `DISCARDED`
- Calls `GET /me/score/{score}/page/{p}/size/{s}` when a score is selected

